      "name": "Affliction",
      "type": "pouvoir",
      "img": "https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg",
      "system": {
        "type": "attaque",
        "activate": true,
        "special": "standard",
        "action": "simple",
        "portee": "contact",
        "duree": "instantane",
        "notes": "<p>You can impose some debilitating condition or conditions on a target by making a close attack. You set the conditions your Affliction causes at each degree when you acquire it and they may not be changed.</p>",
        "effets": "<p>FORTITUDE OR WILL VS. DC [AFFLICTION RANK + 10] SUCCESS: NO EFFECT. FAILURE (ONE DEGREE): THE TARGET IS DAZED, ENTRANCED, FATIGUED, HINDERED, IMPAIRED, OR VULNERABLE (CHOOSE ONE).</p>",
        "effetsprincipaux": "",
        "link": "",
        "descripteurs": {},
        "extras": {
          "2": {
            "name": "Contagious",
            "data": {
              "type": "extra",
              "description": "<p>Contagious effects work on both the target and anyone coming into contact with the target. New targets resist the effect normally.</p><p><br></p><p>+1 cost per Power rank.</p>",
              "cout": {
                "fixe": false,
                "rang": true,
                "value": 1
              }
            },
            "details": true
          },
          "3": {
            "name": "Cumulative (Affliction)",
            "data": {
              "type": "extra",
              "description": "<p>A Cumulative Affliction adds any further degrees to the existing degrees on the target. </p><p><br></p><p>+1 cost per Power rank.</p>",
              "cout": {
                "fixe": false,
                "rang": true,
                "value": 1
              }
            },
            "details": true
          }
        },
        "defauts": {
          "1": {
            "name": "Grab-Based",
            "data": {
              "type": "defaut",
              "description": "<p>An attack with this flaw requires you to successfully grab and hold a target before the effect can be used.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>",
              "cout": {
                "fixe": false,
                "rang": true,
                "value": 1
              }
            },
            "details": true
          },
          "2": {
            "name": "Inaccurate",
            "data": {
              "type": "defaut",
              "description": "<p>An effect with this flaw is hard to control or wildly inaccurate. Each rank gives you a –2 penalty to attack checks.</p><p>Flat -1 point per rank.</p>",
              "cout": {
                "fixe": true,
                "rang": false,
                "value": 2
              }
            },
            "details": true
          }
